OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cloudy start with spots of
OL,6,Frain and drizzle for parts of Cumbria.
OL,7,FA little brighter to the south, though
OL,8,Fthicker cloud and drizzle will slowly
OL,9,Fpush southwards through the day. Windy
OL,10,Fat times. Mild for the time of year.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FMostly cloudy this evening
OL,13,Fand overnight with spots of rain and
OL,14,Fdrizzle continuing. Often windy though
OL,15,Fthe cloud and added breeze will hold
OL,16,Ftemperatures up.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
