OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FA wet and windy day to come
OL,6,Fwith some heavy spells of rain at
OL,7,Ftimes. Very windy around coasts and
OL,8,Fhills. Not as mild, but temperature
OL,9,Fstill above average.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FUnsettled
OL,12,Fwith further rain at times on Friday.
OL,13,FDrier and perhaps brighter on Saturday
OL,14,Fbefore further rain arrives later and
OL,15,Finto Sunday. Often windy with
OL,16,Ftemperatures returning to average.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
